message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "Metadata Audit Simulator"
abstract: >-
  A single-file, in-browser digital-humanities teaching tool for auditing how
  gaps and inconsistencies in cultural-heritage metadata drive AI
  image-generation hallucination. Developed for the ESU 2026 Digital Archives
  workshop. Initial prototype generated with Google Gemini; developed and
  extended with Claude (Anthropic).
type: software
